<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1060117-does-anyone-know-how-much-of-this-book-is">Does anyone know how much of this book is true and how much is fiction? I LOVED this book. If all is true, it is a phenomenal story and even better than fiction.</a>
</div>
